Yuzuru Hanyu of Team Japan finished fourth in the men's single skating free skating final at the 2022 Winter Olympic Games at Capital Indoor Stadium in Beijing on Thursday. Chloe Kim of Team USA won the gold medal in the women's snowboard halfpipe final at the 2022 Winter Olympics at Genting Snow Park H & S Stadium in Zhangjiakou, north China's Hebei Province, on Thursday. Peng Junyue and Huang Yebo of Team China finished 17th in the luge men's doubles event at the 2022 Winter Olympics at Yanqing National Sliding Center in Yanqing District, Beijing on Tuesday. Cai Xuetong of China finished fourth in women's snowboard halfpipe event at Beijing 2022 on Thursday.